### 1. 查询所有用户（GET请求，和浏览器访问一样）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/list
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. 根据ID查询用户（GET请求）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. 测试添加用户：验证「姓名不能重复」的规则
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "age": 22,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 4. 测试添加用户：验证「年龄不能小于0」的规则
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试用户1",
  "age": -5,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### 5. 测试添加用户：验证「密码长度不能少于6位」的规则
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试用户2",
  "age": 22,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 6. 测试添加用户：验证「所有规则都符合，添加成功」
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "李鑫哲",
  "age": 20,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "12345678"
}

###

### 7. 测试修改用户（PUT请求，必须带ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "李鑫哲-修改",
  "age": 21,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "87654321"
}

###

### 8. 测试删除用户（DELETE请求，末尾数字是要删除的用户ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/user/3
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. 条件查询用户：测试年龄>=20的用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. 模糊搜索：查所有姓张的用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search?name=张
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. 范围筛选：查20-30岁的用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search?minAge=20&maxAge=30
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. 精准过滤：只查女性用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search?gender=女
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. 多条件组合：查20-30岁、姓张的男性用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search?name=张&minAge=20&maxAge=30&gender=男
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. 查所有用户，按年龄从大到小排序
GET http://localhost:8080/user/search
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. 基础分页：查第1页，每页2条数据（你的表里有14条数据，会分成7页）
GET http://localhost:8080/user/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=2
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. 分页+搜索：查第1页，每页10条，姓张的用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&name=张
Content-Type: application/json

### 17. 分页+多条件筛选：查第1页，每页10条，20-30岁的女性用户
GET http://localhost:8080/user/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&minAge=20&maxAge=30&gender=女
Content-Type: application/json

### 18. 测试默认值：不传页码和每页条数，默认查第1页、每页10条
GET http://localhost:8080/user/page
Content-Type: application/json

### 19. 测试字段自动填充：添加新用户
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试自动填充",
  "age": 22,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123456"
}
### 20. 测试逻辑删除：删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/user/16
Content-Type: application/json

### 21. 测试全局异常处理：传非数字的ID，触发类型转换异常
GET http://localhost:8080/user/abc
Content-Type: application/json

### 22. 测试参数校验：姓名为空，触发@NotBlank校验
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "age": 22,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 23. 测试参数校验：年龄为负数，触发@Min校验
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试校验",
  "age": -5,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 24. 测试参数校验：密码长度不足6位，触发@Size校验
POST http://localhost:8080/user/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试校验",
  "age": 22,
  "gender": "男",
  "password": "123"
}